info.description:
Complete REST API collection for NYCTaxiData — generated from source code (Controllers, Commands, Queries, DTOs). Covers Auth, Trips, Drivers, Zones, Analytics, AI Predictions, Simulation, and Admin endpoints. JWT Bearer authentication is required for most routes.

Base URL: {{baseUrl}}
Auth: Bearer Token → {{authToken}}

request.description:
Returns per-zone trip statistics aggregated across all zones with separate calculated and predicted fields.

Query: GetZoneStatisticsQuery()
Returns: Result<List<ZoneStatisticsDto>> { zoneId, zoneName, borough, calculated: { totalPickupTrips, totalDropoffTrips, totalRevenue, avgFare, avgTip, busiestHourOfDay, busiestDayOfWeek }, predicted: { expectedDemand15Min, expectedDemand6H, expectedRevenue6H, stockoutProbability, busiestHourForecast } }

Returns peak hour analysis for trip demand with separate calculated and predicted curves.

Query: GetPeakHoursQuery()
Returns: Result<List<TripPeakHoursDto>> { hour, calculatedTripCount, calculatedTotalRevenue, predictedTripCount, predictedTotalRevenue, tripCount, totalRevenue }

Returns overall statistics aggregated across all zones.

Query: GetZoneStatisticsQuery(null)
Returns: Result<ZoneStatisticsDto> { zoneId, zoneName, borough, calculated: { totalPickupTrips, totalDropoffTrips, totalRevenue, avgFare, avgTip, busiestHourOfDay, busiestDayOfWeek }, predicted: { expectedDemand15Min, expectedDemand6H, expectedRevenue6H, stockoutProbability, busiestHourForecast } }

Returns statistics for a specific zone.

Query: GetZoneStatisticsQuery(id)
Returns: Result<ZoneStatisticsDto> { zoneId, zoneName, borough, calculated: { totalPickupTrips, totalDropoffTrips, totalRevenue, avgFare, avgTip, busiestHourOfDay, busiestDayOfWeek }, predicted: { expectedDemand15Min, expectedDemand6H, expectedRevenue6H, stockoutProbability, busiestHourForecast } }

Returns geographic heatmap data for trip pickup/dropoff density across all zones.

Query: GetHeatmapDataQuery()
Returns: Result<List<HeatmapDataPointDto>> { zoneId, zoneName, borough, latitude, longitude, calculatedTripCount, predictedTripCount, predictedStockoutProbability, surgeMultiplier, demandLevel, tripCount }

Compares statistics across multiple zones. Send multiple zoneIds query parameters.

Query: CompareZonesQuery(zoneIds: List<int>)
Returns: Result<ZoneComparisonDto> { comparisonData: List<ZoneStatisticsDto>, highestRevenueZone, busiestZone }

Returns the top recommended zones for driver positioning based on demand.

Query: GetRecommendedZonesQuery(limit)
Returns: Result<List<RecommendedZoneDto>> { zoneId, zoneName, borough, recommendationScore, demandSupplyRatio, predictedRevenueYield, reason, avgFare, avgTip }

Returns peak hours for a specific zone or all zones.

Query: GetPeakHoursQuery(zoneId)
Returns: Result<List<PeakHoursDto>> { hour, calculatedTripCount, calculatedTotalRevenue, calculatedAverageFare, predictedTripCount, predictedTotalRevenue, predictedAverageFare, tripCount, totalRevenue, averageFare }

Returns the top zones ranked by demand.

Query: GetTopDemandZonesQuery(limit)
Returns: Result<List<TopDemandZoneDto>> { zoneId, zoneName, borough, calculatedPickups, percentageOfTotalCalculated, predictedPickups, percentageOfTotalPredicted, pickupCount, percentageOfTotal }

Returns the top zones ranked by revenue generated.

Query: GetTopRevenueZonesQuery(limit)
Returns: Result<List<TopRevenueZoneDto>> { zoneId, zoneName, borough, calculatedRevenue, percentageOfTotalCalculated, predictedRevenue, percentageOfTotalPredicted, totalRevenue, percentageOfTotal }

Returns zones with the highest risk of driver stockout (supply shortage).

Query: GetHighStockoutZonesQuery(limit)
Returns: Result<List<HighStockoutZoneDto>> { zoneId, zoneName, borough, calculatedPickupCount, calculatedAvailableDriversCount, calculatedDeficitCount, calculatedStockoutProbability, predictedPickupCount, predictedAvailableDriversCount, predictedDeficitCount, predictedStockoutProbability, pickupCount, availableDriversCount, deficitCount, stockoutProbability }
